{"id":232303668,"title":"#分享   goshare APP桃園有gogoro的共享電動車!!","content":"GoShare首波在桃園都會地區投放約一千輛共享電動機車，位於「桃園區，中壢區，八德區，長庚醫院附近，桃園高鐵附近」可以騎超過區域範圍，但是要結束騎乘得在上述區域內，否則無法還車要特別注意\n\n之前一直有看過Gogoro而沒有真的騎過，透過這次Goshare的騎乘體驗，沒想到電動機車騎乘的速度感不輸給一般機車，而且APP操作其實很好上手，介面簡單流暢，不得不佩服Gogoro這家公司\n\n比較可惜的是目前只有在桃園部分區域試行，範圍還沒有很大，另外對於身高比較高的人，騎乘時腳無法往前伸長，其實不太舒服，希望未來改版的車是否能調整。\n\n對於整體的體驗還是不錯的，如果有考慮要換電動車的人真的可以考慮一下Gogoro，或者直接下載GoShare先來體驗看看\n\n文章網址裡有goshare優惠卷可以領取喔\n\n文章出處:https://www.samchoulove.com/use-goshare/ \n\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/M4AMTKV.jpg\nhttp://i.imgur.com/SqtFSfc.jpg","excerpt":"GoShare首波在桃園都會地區投放約一千輛共享電動機車，位於「桃園區，中壢區，八德區，長庚醫院附近，桃園高鐵附近」可以騎超過區域範圍，但是要結束騎乘得在上述區域內，否則無法還車要特別注意，之前一直有","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"577f29b9-ef96-4e05-9e79-55e2a7d6e3db","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-10-15T12:31:56.555Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-15T12:31:56.555Z","commentCount":0,"likeCount":4,"tags":[],"topics":["GoShare","Gogoro","共享電動車"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"App","forumAlias":"app","school":"Simon08","department":"simon08","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":4}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/M4AMTKV.jpg"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/SqtFSfc.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"11c9c690-e38e-4969-bb85-3c0f10e9db9d","url":"https://i.imgur.com/M4AMTKVl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/M4AMTKVl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/M4AMTKVl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-10-15T12:31:56.555Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-15T12:31:56.555Z"},{"id":"11c9c690-e38e-4969-bb85-3c0f10e9db9d","url":"http://i.imgur.com/M4AMTKV.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/M4AMTKV","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/M4AMTKVl.jp